title: Independent candidate Haji Imtiaz wins NA-68 seat
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Haji Imtiaz Ahmed has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-68 MB Din-I by securing 166,093 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Mushahid Raza of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) who bagged 70,926 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 50.01 percent.
